9 An Act relating to Presidential Electors; amending 26
O.S. 2021, Section 10-108, which relates to
10 vacancies; updating statutory language; prescribing
oath for Electors filling vacancies; and providing an
11 effective date.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 10-108, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 In the event any Presidential Elector fails to meet at the
18 Governor’s office at the prescribed time or refuses or fails to vote
19 for the persons nominated for the offices of President and Vice
20 President by the political party which that nominated the
21 Presidential Elector, it shall be the duty of the Electors present
22 at the prescribed time and place aforesaid to shall appoint a person
23 to fill such vacancy. The person appointed to fill the vacancy
24 shall subscribe to an oath stating that the appointee will cast a
SB1491 HFLR Page 1
