1 ball ot for the persons nominated for the offices of President and
2 Vice President by the appointee’s political party. The oath shall
3 be witnessed by the Governor or the Governor’s designee and filed
4 with the Secretary of State.
5 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
6
